element_texts.text:
[penciled note, by archivist?:] Light, Jim?
[printed postcard text:]
Holiday Inn
9360 Wilshire Blvd.
Beverly Hills, California
Resv. (213) 273-1400
"In the heart of Beverly Hills"
[postmark date: Dec. 31, 1982]
Dear Sage,
Greetings from the land of tinsel and glitter. Enjoying 70 [degree] sunny weather but lots of smog. Have seen a number of big stars on the studio lots. Going to many big special screenings and trying to stay clear of the hookers on the sunset strip. Off to Mexico tomorrow. Hope you have a good New Year. Love, [Jim?]
[to:]
Dr. Jack Conroy 
701 Fisk
Moberly, MO 65270

Greetings
from Brendan Light as well as Jim and Amy
